The report shall include the following information:
For each approved project:
The name of the approved company and a brief description of the project;
The amount of approved costs included in the agreement;
The maximum amount of incentives the approved company may recover over the term of the agreement;
The term of the agreement; and
The total amount recovered under the agreement, reported for both the prior fiscal year and cumulatively;
The number of applications for projects submitted during the prior fiscal year;
The number of projects finally approved during the prior fiscal year; and
The total dollar amount approved for recovery for all projects approved during the prior fiscal year, and cumulatively under the Tourism Development Act since its inception, by year of approval.
